<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error: <%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .error-card {
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
            background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="card error-card p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h1 class="card-title text-danger mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-x-octagon-fill me-2"></i>
                    Error en la Aplicación
                </h1>
                
                <h2 class="fs-4 text-warning mb-3"><%= title %></h2>
                
                <p class="card-text text-light">Se ha producido un error inesperado durante el procesamiento de su solicitud:</p>
                
                <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                    <pre class="mb-0 text-break" style="white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; border: none; color: inherit;"><%= error %></pre>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-secondary small">Si el problema persiste, contacta con el administrador del sistema o intenta <a href="/auth/google" class="text-info">iniciar sesión nuevamente</a>.</p>
                
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light mt-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-house-door-fill me-2"></i>
                    Volver a la Página Principal
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>